Description:
List ofAction to be taken on the port_handle selected.
Valid options are:
set_factory_defaults: resets the port to factory default.
remove_protocol: removes the protocol config on the port specified by the protocol argument
List of port_handles on which to act

Constants: bfd, bgp, cfm, eigrp, igmp, isis, lacp, ldp, efm, mld, mplstp, ospfv2, ospfv3, pim, rip, ripng, rsvp, static, stp, all
